 169:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c **** /**
 170:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @brief  Perform a mass erase or erase the specified FLASH memory pages.
 171:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @note   Before any operation, it is possible to check there is no operation suspended
 172:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *         by call HAL_FLASHEx_IsOperationSuspended()
 173:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @param[in]  pEraseInit Pointer to an @ref FLASH_EraseInitTypeDef structure that
 174:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *         contains the configuration information for the erasing.
 175:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @param[out]  PageError Pointer to variable that contains the configuration
 176:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *         information on faulty page in case of error (0xFFFFFFFF means that all
 177:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *         the pages have been correctly erased)
 178:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   * @retval HAL Status
